{
  "stem": "5810.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And how wonderful it would be to just go there and see if by any chance anyone that I knew before the war would be there, because a, a French ball, which was also attended by some Belgians, that would be a good place to, to see if any, any anybody would have survived this.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because the one thing that I did not have, to go back some, is that anyone that was hidden in orphanages and convents and in group situation, at least after the war, they had somebody that they knew during the war that they reunited with and they had their own support group that way.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Having been hidden in a single family and alone, I had no one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I, I, I had nothing and nobody, nobody that I knew, nobody that I could've made friends with or survived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to that French ball and it turned out that I did meet somebody that knew a mutual friend I knew-- that I had met right after the war liberation time, who is still alive today.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's my only friend from Belgium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was my age and he went through pretty much the same thing I did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Although we, having worked together-- hidden children, the unusual thing is that we never spoke about, our hiding experience.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the most unusual thing, and I only discovered that later, that how could we have worked and known each other now for 45 years and having worked together for about nine years, and we never spoke about our hidden experience.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But neither did I do it with my sister, so-- but that's another story.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, I, I--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
